      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46) in factory-correct Alpine White. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Mechanically flawless, the VANOS system has been bulletproofed, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to ensure structural rigidity. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping characteristics, while the variable M differential lock provides optimal torque vectoring. With zero cosmetic imperfections and a documented service history, this chassis maintains its high-revving linear power delivery and telepathic handling. A true purist\u2019s specimen in concours condition.",
